The Cheyenne Mountain Complex is one of the icons of the Cold War
It was home to the North American Aerospace Command -LRB- NORAD -RRB-
The high tech base entered popular culture with appearances in the 1983 Cold War thriller War Games and 1994 's Stargate
The Cheyenne Mountain Complex is home to more than 1,000 personnel and is able to operate as an underground town for months with fresh water and food
